.'=>'from these notifications.','Unsubscribe'=>'Unsubscribe',' for more information on our premium services, which can automatically block and detect malicious IP addresses.'=>' for more information on our premium services, which can automatically block and detect malicious IP addresses.','Limit Login Attempts Reloaded website'=>'Limit Login Attempts Reloaded website','Unfortunately, we cannot determine the severity of the IP address with the free version of the plugin. If the IP continues to make attempts and is not recognized by your organization, then it\'s likely to have malicious intent. Depending on how frequent the attacks are, you may experience performance issues. In the plugin dashboard, you can investigate the frequency of the failed login attempts in the logs and take additional steps to protect your website (i.e. adding them to the block list). You can visit the '=>'Unfortunately, we cannot determine the severity of the IP address with the free version of the plugin. If the IP continues to make attempts and is not recognised by your organisation, then it\'s likely to have malicious intent. Depending on how frequent the attacks are, you may experience performance issues. In the plugin dashboard, you can investigate the frequency of the failed login attempts in the logs and take additional steps to protect your website (i.e. adding them to the block list). You can visit the ','How dangerous is this failed login attempt?'=>'How dangerous is this failed login attempt?','You are receiving this email because there was a failed login attempt on your website {domain}. If you\'d like to opt out of these notifications, please click the “Unsubscribe” link below.'=>'You are receiving this email because there was a failed login attempt on your website {domain}. If you\'d like to opt out of these notifications, please click the “Unsubscribe” link below.','Why am I getting these emails?'=>'Why am I getting these emails?','A failed login attempt is when an IP address uses incorrect credentials to log into your website. The IP address could be a human operator, or a program designed to guess your password.'=>'A failed login attempt is when an IP address uses incorrect credentials to log into your website. The IP address could be a human operator, or a program designed to guess your password.','What is a failed login attempt?'=>'What is a failed login attempt?','Frequently Asked Questions'=>'Frequently Asked Questions','Go to Dashboard'=>'Go to Dashboard','Please visit your WordPress dashboard for additional details, investigation options, and help articles.'=>'Please visit your WordPress dashboard for additional details, investigation options, and help articles.','IP was blocked for {blocked_duration}'=>'IP was blocked for {blocked_duration}','Last user attempted: <b>{username}</b>'=>'Last user attempted: <b>{username}</b>','{attempts_count} failed login attempts ({lockouts_count} lockout(s)) from IP <b>{ip_address}</b>'=>'{attempts_count} failed login attempts ({lockouts_count} lockout(s)) from IP <b>{ip_address}</b>','The failed login details include:'=>'The failed login details include:','This is installed on your <b>{domain}</b> WordPress site.'=>'This is installed on your <b>{domain}</b> WordPress site.','Hello,'=>'Hello,','Hello {name},'=>'Hello {name},','Warning: Your site has experienced over 100 failed login attempts in the past 24 hours'=>'Warning: Your site has experienced over 100 failed login attempts in the past 24 hours','(past 24 hrs)'=>'(past 24 hrs)','Hooray! Zero failed login attempts (past 24 hrs)'=>'Hooray! Zero failed login attempts (past 24 hrs)','No contract - cancel anytime'=>'No contract - cancel any time','The %s IP range is invalid'=>'The %s IP range is invalid','Add this code to all websites in your network to sync protection (payment required for additional domains unless it\'s with an Agency plan\'s first tier).'=>'Add this code to all websites in your network to sync protection (payment required for